# Infrastructure Standards

## Containerization
- Use multi-stage Docker builds
- Implement proper health checks
- Use non-root users
- Follow container security best practices

## Kubernetes
- Use proper resource requests/limits
- Implement proper probes
- Use proper service mesh integration
- Follow GitOps practices

## CI/CD
- Implement proper testing stages
- Use proper security scanning
- Implement proper deployment strategies
- Use proper environment separation